{"tid":1432393,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"東區醫院餐廳貼大字報　拒給警員用餐優惠","createTime":"2019-08-08T08:33:18.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-08T23:57:31.000Z","uid":184679,"like":101,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"debdcace5512cd302c9717c121a515f15939d2bf","tid":1432393,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T08:33:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static02-proxy.hket.com/res/v3/image/content/2420000/2422068/KakaoTalk_20190808_150709063_1024.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic02-proxy.hket.com%2Fres%2Fv3%2Fimage%2Fcontent%2F2420000%2F2422068%2FKakaoTalk_20190808_150709063_1024.jpg&h=f0ac27d6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n東區醫院職員餐廳疑因不滿《反修例》示威活動期間，警方對示威者的過激行動，據悉，由昨（7 日）起，在餐廳內張貼大字報，抵制警員享用餐廳職員價。事件在網上流傳後，獲得不少網民支持，並讚揚職員。<br />\n<br />\n根據資料，東區醫院餐廳一向是由「泛亞」承包，「泛亞」是屬大家樂集團旗下公司。TOPick記者現已向大家樂集團了解事件，正等候回覆。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static02-proxy.hket.com/res/v3/image/content/2420000/2422068/KakaoTalk_20190808_150711945_1024.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic02-proxy.hket.com%2Fres%2Fv3%2Fimage%2Fcontent%2F2420000%2F2422068%2FKakaoTalk_20190808_150711945_1024.jpg&h=33e07fc5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲ 東區醫院面對柴灣警署一條行人天橋被貼彩紙，仿如「連儂牆」<br />\n<br />\n此外，東區醫院主座面對柴灣警署的一條行人天橋，被人貼滿「返送中」的彩紙，仿如「連儂牆」，連最新一宗浸大學生會會長方仲賢因購買鐳射筆被捕事件，亦有人人回應指「鐳射筆是武器？我家貓咪話佢唔食呢隻死貓！」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static02-proxy.hket.com/res/v3/image/content/2420000/2422068/KakaoTalk_20190808_150710371_1024.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic02-proxy.hket.com%2Fres%2Fv3%2Fimage%2Fcontent%2F2420000%2F2422068%2FKakaoTalk_20190808_150710371_1024.jpg&h=465fdc0f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲ 有市民貼紙指，有關雷射筆事件，佢隻貓「唔食呢隻死貓」<br />\n<br />\n<pre><code data-type=\"\">https://topick.hket.com/article/2422068/%E3%80%90%E5%8F%8D%E4%BF%AE%E4%BE%8B%E3%80%91%E6%9D%B1%E5%8D%80%E9%86%AB%E9%99%A2%E9%A4%90%E5%BB%B3%E8%B2%BC%E5%A4%A7%E5%AD%97%E5%A0%B1%E3%80%80%E6%8B%92%E7%B5%A6%E8%AD%A6%E5%93%A1%E7%94%A8%E9%A4%90%E5%84%AA%E6%83%A0?mtc=10045</code></pre>"},{"pid":"b9a5d23041fce5918d6042ef8be2a892736edf2d","tid":1432393,"uid":265192,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T08:35:41.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">機場集會徵求以下文宣資源：<br />\n<br />\n1. 警察使用暴力、傷害無辜GIF圖及片段<br />\n2. 外語展示式文宣<br />\n3. 外語派發式文宣</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n請貼到：<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1432384\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1432384</a><br />\n麻煩各位巴打 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4afb78b6fd5ac7164978fe761ebda56e508ddd4f","tid":1432393,"uid":48796,"like":15,"dislike":0,"score":15,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T08:47:53.000Z","msg":"東區醫院餐廳竟然被黃屍滲透! <br />\n本人深藍立場, 予以強烈譴責!  <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/argue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n警隊熱心服務巿民, 餐廳應該大字標題: <br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">歡迎警員! 凍撚水任飲! </span> <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aee20b8a2539754016afe589b5414be7291348f0","tid":1432393,"uid":240960,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T08:50:53.000Z","msg":"擺明醫院職員餐廳啦 憑乜撚野着住套狗衫有職員價呀"},{"pid":"c3e87a3a094c12221019c344332e8aac35bf9fa4","tid":1432393,"uid":125680,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"aee20b8a2539754016afe589b5414be7291348f0","tid":1432393,"uid":240960,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T08:50:53.000Z","msg":"擺明醫院職員餐廳啦 憑乜撚野着住套狗衫有職員價呀"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T08:52:01.000Z","msg":"真"},{"pid":"8e79e872a30c9358bec883e8155be4aa6ac2ee60","tid":1432393,"uid":133743,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T08:52:25.000Z","msg":"其實跟規矩警察係唔應該有醫院員工優惠wor"},{"pid":"af55f7962b8ce728ff7ccdb